<treatmentCitation author="Cowie" box="[660,990,1733,1758]" page="79" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" year="2003">
<bibRefCitation author="Cowie" box="[660,990,1733,1758]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" refString="Cowie, R. H. &amp; Thiengo, S. C. (2003) The apple snails of the Americas (Mollusca: Gastropoda: Ampullariidae: Asolene, Felipponea, Marisa, Pomacea, Pomella): a nomenclatural and type catalog. Malacologia, 45 (1), 41 - 100. [29 August; Malacologia 46 (1); un-numbered page at end of issue]" type="journal article" year="2003">
